OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FEngland earned a commanding 4-2
OL,7,Fvictory against Croatia in a statement
OL,8,FWorld Cup opener on Wednesday evening.
OL,10,FThree Lions fans had their eyes on the
OL,11,FDallas Cowboys' AT&T Stadium as Thomas
OL,12,FTuchel's team got their campaign up
OL,13,Fand running.
OL,15,FIt was all square at half-time after a
OL,16,Fblockbuster first 45 minutes with a
OL,17,FHarry Kane brace matched by goals from
OL,18,FMartin Baturina and Petar Musa.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FEngland were pegged back twice after
OL,7,FKane opened the scoring with a retaken
OL,8,Fpenalty.
OL,10,FTwo minutes after the restart, Jude
OL,11,FBellingham put England in front with a
OL,12,Fclinical finish after a scintillating
OL,13,Frun.
OL,15,FMarcus Rashford applied the finishing
OL,16,Ftouch to the 4-2 win after a sweeping
OL,17,FEngland attack in the 85th minute.
OL,19,FThree Lions supporters were very vocal
OL,20,Fduring the game, including loudly
OL,21,Fbooing the mid-half drinks breaks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FFIFA said it was unaware of any
OL,7,Fsupporters entering the stadium
OL,8,Fwithout tickets after eyewitnesses
OL,9,Fclaimed scores of fans breached
OL,10,Fsecurity and entered the venue without
OL,11,Fchecks.
OL,13,FThe official attendance announced for
OL,14,Fthe game was 70,389, just under the
OL,15,F70,649 official capacity confirmed pre-
OL,16,Ftournament by FIFA.
OL,18,FOutside the stadium, England fans were
OL,19,Fin a jubilant mood following their
OL,20,Fside's victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
