CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FCambridge United supporters Chris
OL,7,FBarrett, 37, and Craig Roberts, 36,
OL,8,Fsaid they believed England have a good
OL,9,Fchance of going all the way in the
OL,10,Ftournament after watching inside the
OL,11,Fair-conditioned venue.
OL,13,FMr Barrett said: "We've always got the
OL,14,Fchance of going all the way."
OL,26,@uD@ROUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FMr Roberts, who described the AT&T
OL,7,FStadium as the best he had ever been
OL,8,Fin, added: "Semi-finals minimum we
OL,9,Fshould be looking at ` if you play
OL,10,FFrance and Spain that's a 50/50 game
OL,11,Fand you need a bit of luck because
OL,12,Fthey're good teams.
OL,14,F"But I think we should beat everyone,
OL,15,Fwe've got a pretty good run if we top
OL,16,Fthe group. So I think we should beat
OL,17,Feveryone up until the semi-finals and,
OL,18,Fas I say, it's a coin toss from there,
OL,19,Fbut we've definitely got it in us."
OL,26,@pD@LOUvD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
