OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FFans who endured scorching
OL,7,Ftemperatures in queues outside the
OL,8,Fstadium were rewarded with a
OL,9,Fcommanding display.
OL,11,FA light breeze did nothing to lessen
OL,12,Fthe strength of the Texas sunshine as
OL,13,Fmany fans tried to make the most of
OL,14,Fwhat little shade trees provided.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FCommenting on how they've coped with
OL,7,Fthe scorching temperatures, Mr Roberts
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association: "The air-
OL,9,Fcon definitely helps, it's boiling out
OL,10,Fhere. Stepping out here you get a gust
OL,11,Fof it and you really feel it. Inside
OL,12,Fit's still warm but it's much better
OL,13,Fthan out here, it makes a massive
OL,14,Fdifference."
OL,16,FMr Barrett added: "The beers, they do
OL,17,Fyou wonders."
OL,19,FThe pair said they planned to attend
OL,20,Fthe Three Lions' final group game
OL,21,Fagainst Panama in New Jersey.
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@LO]xD@SOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
