CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FAsked if they would be coming back if
OL,7,FEngland progressed far in the
OL,8,Ftournament, Mr Roberts said: "I think
OL,9,FI'd have to sell my house."
OL,11,FMr Barrett added: "We'll see what
OL,12,Fhappens. We'll see what the Mrs says."
OL,14,FAn Englishman who lives in Missouri
OL,15,Fsaid England's performance was "one of
OL,16,Fthe best" he had seen.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@[O]sD@SOUtD@fO]wD@`OUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
