OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FStoke-on-Trent-born John Bath, 46, who
OL,7,Fattended the game with his wife
OL,8,FChelsea Bath and their two children,
OL,9,Fsaid: "That was a solid performance
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,F"I think that was one of the best
OL,13,Fperformances England has put in for as
OL,14,Flong as I can remember ` five to 10
OL,15,Fyears at least.
OL,17,F"They passed the ball around well,
OL,18,Fthey looked sharp, (Marcus) Rashford
OL,19,Fgetting a goal at the end."
OL,26,@qD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
