SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FChelsea, a 42-year-old American
OL,7,Fcitizen, said she had "converted
OL,8,Fcompletely" to supporting England
OL,9,Falongside her family.
OL,11,FShe said: "It was amazing, it was
OL,12,Fincredible, 4-2. It's a good way to go
OL,13,Fhome, we're happy. I've converted
OL,14,Fcompletely ` 100%."
OL,16,FBefore the game, fans arrived hours
OL,17,Fbefore kick-off and queued in the
OL,18,Fscorching Arlington sunshine.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@KO]sD@KOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
