PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FA Texas-based England fan, Tammy
OL,7,FMurphy, said she was "melting" with
OL,8,Fthe rest of the Three Lions fans in
OL,9,Fthe queue ahead of the game.
OL,11,FThe Chelsea supporter told PA: "Oh
OL,12,Fit's miserable for us too ` it's
OL,13,Fmiserable, the humidity out here...
OL,14,Feven though you guys are melting,
OL,15,Fwe're melting with you. Nobody likes
OL,16,Fthis."
OL,18,FOne England fan who waited in the
OL,19,Fqueue to get into the stadium said he
OL,20,Fpaid #6,000 for two front-row tickets
OL,21,Fto the match.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@^O]sD@`OUxD@FO]
