OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781750864
OL,3,CEngland fans delighted by win over
OL,4,CCroatia in opening World Cup match
OL,6,FMartin Mulholland, originally from
OL,7,FRugby, Warwickshire, but who now lives
OL,8,Fin North Carolina, said: "I think we
OL,9,Fbought tickets at a really, really bad
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"We're in the front row, so we've got
OL,13,Fgood ones, but it was #6,000 for two
OL,14,Ftickets."
